y</i> (as opposed to   Harry  ) become the standard vernacular form, mainly under the influence of the Latin form <i>Henricus</i> and French <i>Henri</i>."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Henry Burton was born in 1300, in Devon, England, United Kingdom as the son of John Burton. He had at least 1 son with Elsa Jessie Burton. He died in his hometown."},"et":{"1300–":"1300–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1299–Female":"1299–Surnud","1324–1357":"1324–1357","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","1324":"1324","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1270":"1270","Halberton, Tiverton, Devon, England":"Halberton, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Devon, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1300–":"1300–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1299–Female":"1299–Kuollut","1324–1357":"1324–1357","1270–Male":"1270–Kuollut","1324":"1324","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1270":"1270","Halberton, Tiverton, Devon, England":"Halberton, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Devon, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1300–":"1300–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1299–Female":"1299–Décédée","1324–1357":"1324–1357","1270–Male":"1270–Décédé","1324":"1324","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1270":"1270","Halberton, Tiverton, Devon, England":"Halberton, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Devon, England":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Henry Burton est né en 1300, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de John Burton. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Elsa Jessie Burton. Il est décédé dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1300–":"1300–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1299–Female":"1299–Verstorben","1324–1357":"1324–1357","1270–Male":"1270–Verstorben","1324":"1324","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1299":"1299","1270":"1270","Halberton, Tiverton, Devon, England":"Halberton, Devon, England, United Kingdom","Devon, England":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Henry Burton wurde 1300 in Devon, England, United Kingdom, a